Changsha, June 19 (XINHUA) -- This capital of

The water level of the river, which flows through Changsha, is still rising sharply, according to local sources.
The flood has caused serious losses to people along both banks of the river, especially in Changsha, according to the sources.
The flood waters had also reached the boulevard along the Xiangjiang River, Xiahe Street and the western part of Zhongshan Street in Changsha proper.
In a telephone call to the Changsha city government, he called on local officials to adopt effective measures, ensure the safety of the lives and property of the residents of Changsha and make an overall success of the work to conquer the flood.
